      "content": "i get that but i've read a lot online that st johns wort is just a natural herb so it's usually pretty mild compared to actual meds. do you really think it's that risky? i mean, i'm only thinking of taking a small dose, not a ton. would it really be an issue if i just took it in the mornings? i just really need something to help me get through these next two weeks of exams.",
